You are in: Home  » Why Us  »  About Us About UsAbove everything else, we never lose sight of the premise that our prosperity is directly linked to yours.
AE Finance Ltd was established in Peterborough nearly 25 years ago by its Managing Director, Salim R Ebrahim FCCA. It not only provides clients with the standard accountancy, audit and taxation services, but also business support and advice, wealth retention, wealth management and strategies for tax planning and mitigation.
AE Finance Limited is able to provide clients with the personal touch.  We have a reputation for our high standards and our fine attention to detail. 
Our dedicated team of qualified client managers and staff members are ready to respond to your requirements. The aim is to offer a pro-active, practical and timely service tailored to the needs of Individuals, Sole Traders, Partnerships, Trusts and Companies.
Our registration with the Association of Chartered Certified Accountants requires us to adopt specific professional standards, which are centrally monitored to ensure compliance. In addition, the Association has introduced a quality assurance accreditation, granted only upon completion of a satisfactory inspection of a firm's quality assurance procedures and professional standards.
In 2003 AE Finance Ltd was awarded the ACCA Quality Checked seal after a rigorous inspection of our existing procedures, becoming one of the few ACCA practitioners then holding this kitemark. We regard this recognition of �best practice' as a significant achievement, and will maintain and indeed improve this level of service, to make quality the hallmark of our practice.  A further visit in 2009 not only re-confirmed the standards maintained but recognised further improvements.

Next Step:
Please contact us if you need further advice, have any questions about our services, would like a free consultation or a fixed fee quote.



 







