Corporate Advisors, Consultants  
and Administrators for Offshore
Companies, Trusts and Free-Zones 
		


 



 









Corporate advisors, administrators, & business setup consultants in Dubai
Alpha Management Limited was incorporated in 2007 in the Dubai International Financial Centre (DIFC) to service the growing regional requirement for tax efficient and effective offshore planning, and company formation in the many “Free Zones” that UAE offers. In addition to company formation and consultancy we offer a variety of corporate services that benefit our clients. From Accounting and Compliance services, to the best advice on Property Purchase structures and DIFC Wills and Probate issues, we have a wealth of knowledge and experience in a variety of areas. Quite often the answer involves the use of one of the above structures. Sometimes the desired effect is achieved simply by re-arranging a client's affairs. We pride ourselves on exploring all avenues before recommending a solution. Our clients are quite surprised that we spend so much time getting to know them, their ventures and priorities. 
 The brightest team of administrators, compliance managers, and business setup consultants at your disposal
Alpha Management can provide clients smart, cost-effective, and efficient business solutions tailored to their needs. Our dynamic and driven team will sit down with you, look into the nature of your need, and develop a bespoke service package tailored to your needs. 
Whether you want to setup a freezone business in Dubai or establish an offshore company, we can assist you. Our consultants work on the basis of transparency towards producing tangible and measurable results. To ensure this, we communicate every piece of information to clients – from the schedule of costs to the processes to be implemented. This way, clients are kept in the loop, every step of the way.
Discuss your needs with Alpha Management’s experienced team of consultants in Dubai. Let us design an approach that benefits you through value-driven solutions. Give us a call or visit our office in DIFC today.Our ServicesOur business revolves around finding individual solutions for your unique set of personal requirements
Offshore Company SetupOffshore Companies are quick to set up, in-expensive and easy to manage.  These types of companies permit 100% foreign ownership, can have bank accounts anywhere in the world and are good for asset holding, international trading, consultancy and investment purposes.
Free Zone Company SetupUAE has over 4 dozen Free Zones, offering specialised environments (i.e.: Internet City, Media City, Health Care City, Knowledge Village) and more generalised environments, such as DMCC, RAK Investment Authority, Ajman Free Zone and many more. Free Zone companies grant investors well-established, reputable and widely recognised investment opportunities for commerce, trading, industrial, service and consulting activities, as well as Residency Visa options. 
DIFC SPCA DIFC Special Purpose Company (SPC) is a private company limited by shares and incorporated under the laws of the DIFC. An SPC has access to the DIFC’s advantageous infrastructure including its own court system which is presided over in English. It is specifically designed to be used in structured finance transactions. 

Other ServicesWe carry out a variety of other services such as Compliance Services, DIFC Wills and Probate, Accounting Services and Property Purchase structures. 

